<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    font-size: 11pt;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 20mm 20mm 20mm 20mm;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #1e40af;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .school-info h2 { font-size: 14pt; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .school-info p  { font-size: 9pt; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.6; }
  .logo { max-height: 60px; max-width: 160px; object-fit: contain; }
  h1 {
    font-size: 14pt;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #1e40af;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 4px;
  }
  .doc-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 9pt;
    color: #64748b;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .sec-heading {
    font-size: 10pt;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #1e40af;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
    padding-bottom: 3px;
    margin: 16px 0 8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  table.info { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
  table.info td {
    padding: 5px 8px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    font-size: 10pt;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
  table.info td:first-child {
    font-weight: bold;
    background: #f8fafc;
    width: 38%;
    color: #334155;
  }
  .checkbox-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 28px;
    padding: 2px 0;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .cb-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 10pt;
  }
  .cb-box {
    font-size: 14pt;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .sig-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 30px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .sig-block { flex: 1; }
  .sig-line {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
    height: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .sig-label { font-size: 9pt; color: #64748b; }
  .hinweis {
    font-size: 9pt;
    color: #374151;
    margin: 14px 0 8px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    background: #f0f9ff;
    border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
    border-radius: 4px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .footer {
    margin-top: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 8pt;
    color: #94a3b8;
    border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    padding-top: 8px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
  <div class="school-info">
    <h2>{{settings.school_name}}</h2>
    <p>
      {{#if settings.school_address}}{{settings.school_address}}<br />{{/if}}
      {{#if settings.school_city}}{{settings.school_city}}<br />{{/if}}
      {{#if settings.school_phone}}Tel.: {{settings.school_phone}}{{#if settings.school_email}} &bull; {{/if}}{{/if}}
      {{#if settings.school_email}}{{settings.school_email}}{{/if}}
      {{#if settings.rlsb}}<br />{{settings.rlsb}}{{/if}}
    </p>
  </div>
  {{#if settings.logo}}
    <img class="logo" src="{{settings.logo}}" alt="Schullogo" />
  {{/if}}
</div>

<h1>Empfangsbest&auml;tigung &uuml;ber den Erhalt eines Leihobjekts</h1>
<p class="doc-subtitle">Bitte sorgf&auml;ltig aufbewahren &mdash; wird bei R&uuml;ckgabe ben&ouml;tigt</p>

<div class="sec-heading">Angaben zum Leihobjekt</div>
<table class="info">
  <tr>
    <td>Ger&auml;teart</td>
    <td>Mobiles Endger&auml;t &nbsp;&#9745;</td>
  </tr>
  <tr><td>Typenbezeichnung</td><td>{{ipad.model}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Seriennummer</td><td style="font-family:monospace">{{ipad.serial}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Inventarnummer</td><td><strong>{{ipad.asset_tag}}</strong></td></tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Bisherige Verleihdauer</td>
    <td>
      <div class="checkbox-row">
        <div class="cb-item"><span class="cb-box">{{#if ipad.rental_age_0}}&#9745;{{else}}&#9744;{{/if}}</span> 0 Jahre</div>
        <div class="cb-item"><span class="cb-box">{{#if ipad.rental_age_1}}&#9745;{{else}}&#9744;{{/if}}</span> 1 Jahr</div>
        <div class="cb-item"><span class="cb-box">{{#if ipad.rental_age_2}}&#9745;{{else}}&#9744;{{/if}}</span> 2 Jahre</div>
        <div class="cb-item"><span class="cb-box">{{#if ipad.rental_age_3}}&#9745;{{else}}&#9744;{{/if}}</span> 3 Jahre</div>
      </div>
    </td>
  </tr>
  {{#if rental.accessories}}
  <tr><td>Zubeh&ouml;r</td><td>{{rental.accessories}}</td></tr>
  {{else}}
  <tr><td>Zubeh&ouml;r</td><td style="color:#94a3b8">keines</td></tr>
  {{/if}}
  <tr><td>Ausgabedatum</td><td>{{rental.lent_date_formatted}}</td></tr>
</table>

<div class="sec-heading">Angaben zum Entleiher</div>
<table class="info">
  {{#if student.is_teacher}}
  <tr><td>Funktion</td><td>Lehrkraft</td></tr>
  {{else}}
  <tr><td>Funktion</td><td>Sch&uuml;lerin / Sch&uuml;ler</td></tr>
  {{/if}}
  <tr><td>Name</td><td><strong>{{student.last_name}}, {{student.first_name}}</strong></td></tr>
  <tr><td>{{student.class_label}}</td><td>{{student.class}}</td></tr>
  {{#if student.moin_username}}<tr><td>Moin.Schule-Benutzername</td><td>{{student.moin_username}}</td></tr>{{/if}}
  {{#unless student.is_teacher}}
  {{#if student.guardian_name}}<tr><td>Erziehungsberechtigte/r</td><td>{{student.guardian_name}}</td></tr>{{/if}}
  {{/unless}}
</table>

<div class="hinweis">
  Mit meiner Unterschrift best&auml;tige ich, das oben genannte Ger&auml;t in dem beschriebenen Zustand erhalten zu haben
  und die Bedingungen des Leihvertrags anerkannt zu haben. Das Ger&auml;t bleibt Eigentum der Schule und ist auf
  Verlangen unverz&uuml;glich zur&uuml;ckzugeben.
</div>

<div class="sec-heading">Unterschriften</div>
{{#if student.is_teacher}}
<div class="sig-row">
  <div class="sig-block">
    <div class="sig-line"></div>
    <div class="sig-label">Ort, Datum &bull; Unterschrift Lehrkraft</div>
  </div>
  <div class="sig-block">
    <div class="sig-line"></div>
    <div class="sig-label">Stempel &amp; Unterschrift Schulleitung</div>
  </div>
</div>
{{else}}
<div class="sig-row">
  <div class="sig-block">
    <div class="sig-line"></div>
    <div class="sig-label">Ort, Datum &bull; Unterschrift Entleiher/in</div>
  </div>
  <div class="sig-block">
    <div class="sig-line"></div>
    <div class="sig-label">Ort, Datum &bull; Unterschrift gesetzliche/r Vertreter/in</div>
  </div>
  <div class="sig-block">
    <div class="sig-line"></div>
    <div class="sig-label">Stempel &amp; Unterschrift Schulleitung</div>
  </div>
</div>
{{/if}}

<div class="footer">
  Erstellt am {{created_date}} &bull; {{settings.school_name}}{{#if settings.rlsb}} &bull; {{settings.rlsb}}{{/if}}
</div>

</body>
</html>
